data.description:
Welcome home! This exquisite brick residence is move in ready and nestled on an impressive corner lot within the highly coveted Ortega Bluff community. 

Conveniently located close to NAS Jax, 2,992 square feet of meticulously designed living space offers both elegance and practicality with an open floor plan, expansive walk in pantry, and nearly a quarter acre of land.

Newer roof and water heater; HVAC Trane system with transferable service plan, and freshly painted walls with premium Behr paint just name a few details that make this home a one of a kind value. Do not delay - schedule your showing today!
